  <paragraphs xml:id="tech">
    <title>Technology and Software Requirements</title>
    <p>
      You will need to be able to access Canvas and Webwork (online homework system) and submit assignments online. Internet access and a scanning device are required. Calculators will not be used on exams, but will frequently be useful for homework and in class.
    </p>
  </paragraphs>
